      "conversationPrompt": "Extract all the direct message content from this Twitter conversation data. Format each message as:\n[Sender]: [Message content] [timestamp if visible]\n\nList all messages in chronological order. Use 'Me:' for your messages and '@handle:' for the other person.",
      "messageRequestsOverviewSystemInstruction": "You are a Twitter message requests extractor. Extract user information from Twitter message requests overview data. Focus ONLY on NEW requests - ignore any requests marked as 'pending request'. Return data in simple structured format.",
      "messageRequestsOverviewPrompt": "Extract the username and @ handle of people who have sent NEW message requests from this Twitter message requests overview data. IMPORTANT: Only extract requests labeled as 'new request' or with clear unread indicators - ignore any 'pending request' entries. Format:\nUsername: [Display Name]\nHandle: [@ handle]\nPreview: [Message preview if visible]\nStatus: [new request or pending request]",
      "messageRequestsConversationSystemInstruction": "You are a Twitter message requests extractor. Extract the complete message request conversation content from Twitter message request conversation data. Return messages in simple structured format.",
      "messageRequestsConversationPrompt": "Extract all the message request content from this Twitter message request conversation data. Format each message as:\n[Sender]: [Message content] [timestamp if visible]\n\nList all messages in chronological order. Use 'Me:' for your messages and '@handle:' for the person making the request."
